| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4166 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d9bf0b54-9b12-59ea-b15c-6e0ca87b2623"
